<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="yes" HEAD="rel-pron" CASE="nominative">who himself</REFEX>
</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 also developed the influential two-level game theory that assumes international agreements will only be successfully brokered if they also result in domestic benefits.
</PARAGRAPH>

<PARAGRAPH>
